name: 3 Piece Wood Pumpkins
description:
2 inch pine with beadboard centers. Perfect!
Use these pumpkins as the decorative focal point of any autumn display or centerpiece. They're perfect from the first crisp day of fall straight through Halloween and Thanksgiving.

Tall 12" tall x 8" wide 
Medium 7" tall x 13" wide
Small 9" x 8 wide

name: Give Thanks Wood Letters
description:
Let these cute letters spell out the meaning of Thanksgiving on a mantel or shelf. Such a wonderful reminder of what it's all about! Each letter is stained and painted differently in beautiful fall colors. 

Approx size of the tallest letter is 8" x 5" wide
please contact me if you would like the exact measurements of each letter

name: Gratitude Wood Letters
description:
“Gratitude, thankfulness, or appreciation is a positive emotion or attitude in acknowledgment of a benefit that one has received or will receive.” What better reminder to have for Thanksgiving or anytime during the year to help us remember to have “an attitude of gratitude.” 

Approx size is 8" tall x 23" wide

This 9 piece set of standing letters can be customized to fit your decor. Convo me with the colors you want and we can create a custom listing.

name: 3 Wood Snowflakes
description:
Bring the winter fun indoors with this delightful set of snowflakes. Standing on a light blue base, these glittered snow flakes will brighten up any room and create an enchanting winter wonderland. Set of three.

Approx sizes are
Tall 17" tall x 5.5" wide 
Medium 14" tall x 5" wide
Small 12" x 4" wide

name: Autumn Acorn
description:
Cut from pine with a bead board shell.
Sanded and distressed for that perfect look!

Approx size is 7" from stem to tip x 5.5" wide
